  planet: 7
  descriptions:
  - 'Incredible! You made it to the finals, you are the only player who ever managed
    to make the Intergalactic championship finals from the first time your planet
    has participated. Managing to beat every opponent is an incredible achievement. '
  - 'However, now it is time to get remembered by the history books. In the finals,
    you will be facing 3 opponents. '
  - 'The planet Kaaman is the place where ArrowHex was invented. They have held planetary
    championships for more than 50,000 Earth years. 3550 years ago their planetary
    championships transformed first into the galactic championship, but soon after
    into the intergalactic championship. '
  - Kaaman holds ArrowHex as almost a sacred game, with it being connected to many
    Kaamanian religious rituals and secular celebrations.
